<item>
  <title>2024 Winter Radio</title>
  <dc:creator>Yunyi Ru</dc:creator>
  <link>https://yunyi-ru.github.io/quarto-blog/music/24winterradio/</link>
  <description><![CDATA[ 




<section id="音乐与我的冬天" class="level1">
<h1>音乐与我的冬天</h1>
<section id="一月" class="level2">
<h2 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="一月">一月</h2>
<ul>
<li>Miserable. 什么都没做只是拼尽全力在和想死的情绪作斗争。</li>
</ul>
</section>
<section id="二月" class="level2">
<h2 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="二月">二月</h2>
<ul>
<li>去看了Alcest，真是太美了，阵容也很完美… 主唱Neige也很美哈哈哈哈。</li>
</ul>
</section>
<section id="三月" class="level2">
<h2 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="三月">三月</h2>
<ul>
<li>刚刚开始，但因为Andy Bell发了让人感觉到春天气息的新专（Pinball Wanderer）我觉得一切都会好起来的。</li>
</ul>
<hr>
</section>
</section>
<section id="我的冬日专辑" class="level1 page-columns page-full">
<h1>我的冬日专辑</h1>
<section id="alcest---les-chants-de-laurore" class="level2 page-columns page-full">
<h2 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="alcest---les-chants-de-laurore">Alcest - Les Chants de l’Aurore</h2>

<div class="no-row-height column-margin column-container"><div class="">
<p><img src="https://yunyi-ru.github.io/quarto-blog/music/covers/alcest2024.jpg" class="img-fluid"></p>
</div></div><p><em>‘Ta main contre la mienne/Les mémoires incandescentes/De ton visage rieur/Et tout pour pouvoir les revivre’</em></p>
<p>一个字也听不懂但就是很美，很喜欢，Flamme Jumelle让我想到了身边逝去的人，与我渐行渐远的人，还有再也无法触及的回忆…</p>
<p><em><strong>推荐曲目：</strong>Flamme Jumelle/Amethyste</em></p>
</section>
<section id="lana-del-rey---ultraviolence" class="level2 page-columns page-full">
<h2 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="lana-del-rey---ultraviolence">Lana Del Rey - Ultraviolence</h2>

<div class="no-row-height column-margin column-container"><div class="">
<p><img src="https://yunyi-ru.github.io/quarto-blog/music/covers/ultraviolence.jpg" class="img-fluid"></p>
</div></div><p><em>‘My boyfriend’s pretty cool/But he’s not as cool as me’</em></p>
<p>因为春天来了，所以开始重温16岁的时候听的东西…感觉自己像个自我感觉良好的沉浸在自己脑内幻想中的bitch，这就是我想有的心态。</p>
<p><em><strong>推荐曲目：</strong>Brooklyn Baby/Black Beauty</em></p>
<p>https://i.scdn.co/image/ab67616d0000b27389a392107ebd79818022b3ea</p>
</section>
<section id="mazzy-star---so-tonight-that-i-might-see" class="level2 page-columns page-full">
<h2 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="mazzy-star---so-tonight-that-i-might-see">Mazzy Star - So Tonight that I Might See</h2>

<div class="no-row-height column-margin column-container"><div class="">
<p><img src="https://yunyi-ru.github.io/quarto-blog/music/covers/mazzystar3.jpg" class="img-fluid"></p>
</div></div><p><em>‘There is a blue light in my best friend’s room/There is a blue light in his eye/There is a blue light, yeah/I want to see it shine’</em></p>
<p>孤独安静又浪漫，听得我非常非常想去加州（以及学滑棒吉他）。</p>
<p><em><strong>推荐曲目：</strong>Fade Into You/Five String Serenade/Blue Light</em></p>


</section>
</section>

 ]]></description>
